race.comment: MAYBE NEXT WEEK (8) ran a respectable 22.73 when filling a minor placing over 401m at this track last start. Hard to top on the time from last start. ZIPPING HILDA (3) has a strong record here with six wins and four placings from 11 starts. In the money last time at this track (22.95) in a Grade 5, finishing a 1.75 lengths third. Looks one of the chances. MIDNIGHT STAR (2) was among the minors three back at this track then missed the frame the last two, but drawn box 2 this time where she has three wins. Has the ability and can find best this time. LUCKY WINNER (7) hit the frame here last time and looks a chance again.
